Pre-Apocalypse[]: Nothing is known about Quintana's life prior to or as the outbreak began.
Post-Apocalypse[]: At some point during the outbreak, Quintana joined a community in Ohio. Quintana is present at the "Kill House" along with his fellow trainees. He is ordered to team up with Johnson by Mercer . With the city breached and many civilians killed as reported by Colonel Vickers and the screams heard throughout the invasion, Quintana's fate is left unknown. It is possible he was let into the Estates with the crowd of terrified citizens or was rescued later on elsewhere in the city, or was killed by the undead.
